				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Launched when player interacts with an item with one of the following root templates.\r\nDEC_GEN_StuffedBear_Standing_A_f8d74269-6a5c-461e-8907-2e1a7b18e1ca\r\nDEC_GEN_StuffedBear_Standing_B_8177353f-5beb-4120-85ec-a4fa261795ae\r\nDEC_GEN_StuffedBear_Standing_C_d760ca77-927c-4880-98a2-991926cdd2a3\r\n\r\n First a skill check roll is done, then the AD is launched. Global flag GLO_TemplateUseSkillCheck_StuffedBear_Success can be used to check if the roll was successful"
				}
